      "rationale": "All 11 constructs tested at the single ASTM F1717-specified offset distance of 50 mm and a single crosshead displacement rate of 5 mm/min. No variation in offset distance or load rate was explored. The required Gradation 3 calls for at least two independent test conditions bracketing the COU envelope; only one condition was applied. Achieved level is Gradation 2. This shortfall is acknowledged and accepted on the basis that the F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard condition and that all three QoI acceptance criteria are satisfied within tight margins. The assessment team judges the remaining uncertainty to be bounded by the validation uncertainty metric (E/uval < 1.96 for all QoI).",
